# Tools

Some simple tools for my own productivity.

---

## pass - Password Store Replacement

Windows-compatible `pass` (password-store) replacement in Go.

### Build
```bash
cd pass
go build -o pass.exe .  # Windows
go build -o pass .     # Linux/macOS
```

### Install
```bash
# Windows: copy pass.exe to PATH
copy pass\pass.exe C:\Windows\System32\

# Linux/macOS:
sudo cp pass/pass /usr/local/bin/
```

### Test
```bash
# Run tests
cd pass
go test ./...

# Manual test
./pass.exe ls
./pass.exe find gmail
./pass.exe insert test/password
```

### Usage
```bash
pass ls                    # List passwords
pass find gmail            # Search
pass email/gmail.com/user  # Show password
pass -c email/...          # Copy to clipboard
pass insert email/...      # Add new password
```

### Prerequisites
- Go 1.20+
- GnuPG (GPG4Win on Windows)
- Git (optional, for version control)

